# Cross-origin isolation — enables SharedArrayBuffer, which the Pyodide
# playground uses to bridge a blocking input() to the terminal.
# The site loads no cross-origin subresources except the Pyodide CDN
# (which sends CORP headers), so applying this site-wide is safe and keeps
# client-side navigation isolated.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp

# The generated social image has no file extension; label its content type.
/opengraph-image
  Content-Type: image/png
